      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sound 2016 BMW M2 (F87) powered by the N55B30T0 3.0L TwinPower Turbo inline-six. This example features the 7-speed M Double Clutch Transmission (M-DCT) with Drivelogic, providing instantaneous torque interruption and crisp gear synchronization. The chassis dynamics are anchored by the Active M Differential and forged aluminum suspension components, ensuring precise turn-in and high-speed stability. Recent service includes a comprehensive fluid flush and a cooling system pressure test. While the exterior shows minor evidence of its 365hp pedigree, the engine remains in peak operating condition with no signs of boost leakage or wastegate rattle. A true driver's spec for those who value mechanical feedback and a linear power band.",
